    "<span class=\"word\">And ye have not his word abiding in you: for whom he hath sent, him ye believe not.</span>",
    "<span class=\"word\">Search the scriptures; for in them ye think ye have eternal life: and they are they which testify of me.</span>",
    "<span class=\"word\">And ye will not come to me, that ye might have life.</span>",
    "<span class=\"word\">I receive not honour from men.</span>",
    "<span class=\"word\">But I know you, that ye have not the love of God in you.</span>",
    "<span class=\"word\">I am come in my Father's name, and ye receive me not: if another shall come in his own name, him ye will receive.</span>",
