    "And when they had found him on the other side of the sea, they said unto him, Rabbi, when camest thou hither?",
    "<span class=\"person\">Jesus</span> answered them and said, <span class=\"word\">Verily, verily, I say unto you, Ye seek me, not because ye saw the miracles, but because ye did eat of the loaves, and were filled.</span>",
