    "<span class=\"person\">Jesus</span> therefore answered and said unto them, <span class=\"word\">Murmur not among yourselves.</span>",
    "<span class=\"word\">No man can come to me, except the Father which hath sent me draw him: and I will raise him up at the last day.</span>",
    "<span class=\"word\">It is written in the prophets, And they shall be all taught of God. Every man therefore that hath heard, and hath learned of the Father, cometh unto me.</span>",
