    "<span class=\"word\">This is that bread which came down from heaven: not as your fathers did eat manna, and are dead: he that eateth of this bread shall live for ever.</span>",
    "These things said he in the synagogue, as he taught in <span class=\"place\">Capernaum</span>.",
