    "<span class=\"word\">It is the spirit that quickeneth; the flesh profiteth nothing: the words that I speak unto you, they are spirit, and they are life.</span>",
    "<span class=\"word\">But there are some of you that believe not.</span> For <span class=\"person\">Jesus</span> knew from the beginning who they were that believed not, and who should betray him.",
