    "<span class=\"word\">And whosoever liveth and believeth in me shall never die. Believest thou this?</span>",
    "She saith unto him, Yea, Lord: I believe that thou art the <span class=\"person\">Christ</span>, the Son of God, which should come into the world.",
    "And when she had so said, she went her way, and called <span class=\"person\">Mary</span> her sister secretly, saying, The Master is come, and calleth for thee.",
